software-center (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of Debian Base Kit Software Center.
  * Native GTK4 and Premium Webview frontends.
  * DBus system service for secure package management.
  * Integrated Flatpak and AppStream support.
  * Automatic system snapshots via Timeshift/Snapper.

 -- Debian Base Kit Team <team@debianbasekit.org>  Sat, 07 Feb 2026 11:00:00 +0000
